parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may deploy unexpectedly.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated
the airbag light is flashing
the airbag did not deploy in an accident
the airbag deployed unexpectedly
the horn failed to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or inability to repair the airbag system due to unavailable parts can lead to continued exposure to the risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: The dealership is unable to repair the airbag system due to unavailable parts
the manufacturer is unable to provide a timeline for part availability
the consumer is unable to get a rental car
the consumer is forced to stop driving the vehicle due to safety concerns.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can lead to the airbag system malfunctioning, which can result in serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger side airbag sensor indicator is illuminated
the airbag sensor failed and needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front coil spring can cause the tire to blow out, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The coil spring breaks or fractures
causing the tire to blow out or become uneven
leading to vibration or shaking while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lower control arm can cause the wheel to become loose, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The lower control arm breaks or fractures
causing the wheel to become loose or fall off
leading to vibration or shaking while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear coil spring can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The rear coil spring breaks or fractures
causing the vehicle to become unstable or vibrate while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension and steering components can cause loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or shakes while driving
or the steering becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power steering light is on
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle makes a clunking or popping noise when turning
the steering wheel feels loose or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel makes a clunking or popping noise when turning
the steering wheel feels loose or unstable
the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power steering light is on
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle makes a clunking or popping noise when turning
the steering wheel feels loose or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the airbag light is on
the ignition system makes a clicking or grinding noise.
